                      <article id="post-166994" class="post-166994 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-blog category-trade-and-manufacturing clearfix with-entry-wrap homepage noimage" data-post_url='http://ourfuture.org/20150206/enormous-humongous-december-trade-deficit-shows-flaws-in-free-trade-log'>												
                            
<div class="entry-wrap">

    
		<header class="entry-header ic_post">	
			<h2 class="entry-title longtitle"><a href="http://ourfuture.org/20150206/enormous-humongous-december-trade-deficit-shows-flaws-in-free-trade-log" title="Enormous, Humongous Trade Deficits Widen, Further Exposing Failed Policy" rel="bookmark" itemprop="name">Enormous, Humongous Trade Deficits Widen, Further Exposing Failed Policy</a></h2>
	    	<time class="entry-date_new" datetime="2015-02-06T08:09:00+00:00" title="February 6, 2015">February 6, 2015</time>
		</header>
     
		<div class="entry-content" data-post_url='http://ourfuture.org/20150206/enormous-humongous-december-trade-deficit-shows-flaws-in-free-trade-log' itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article">
	
            The U.S. has run huge trade deficits for decades since the "free trade" ideology came to dominate. The world's economy needs honestly, democratically and transparently negotiated trade agreements.		   </div><!--  entry-content -->
	
    <footer class="entry-meta">
